channel.title: E/E - 2050 AD [EDM, Progressive House, Future Bass]
channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/eslashe/2050-ad
"Welcome To The Future" with 2050 AD, a blend of Future Bass and Progressive House. Featuring a quick upbeat tempo, diverse rhythms and a pounding drop, tied together by a simple and sweet melodic line that leaves a strong impact, this song is certainly not from the current time period.
